Dialogue: 0,00:00:55.35,00:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost 300 ryo, thanks \Nto your meddling.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:58.81,00:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't go back empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:01.60,00:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If your hands are so \Nempty, will you hold this?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:33.18,00:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true they hired you \Nfor only twenty ryo?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:36.43,00:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:38.18,00:01:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword we stole was a treasure \Ngiven to them by the Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:42.39,00:01:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll only pay \Ntwenty to get it back?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.36,00:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:49.44,00:01:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a poor, small clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.86,00:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to swindle 300 ryo for \Na sword is asking too much.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.32,00:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:02.83,00:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a nasty \Nstorm's brewing...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:05.37,00:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't waste my time here!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.34,00:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Scroll
Dialogue: 0,00:03:19.87,00:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:22.28,00:03:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one hell of a storm!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.16,00:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! My roof got blown \Noff and scared my wife so bad...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.16,00:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...that she went into labor.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:29.08,00:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really something.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:30.75,00:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your seventh kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:33.13,00:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, the ninth.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:34.63,00:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You must really \Nlove your wife!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:39.43,00:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Sakichi's daughter \Nfrom Shimoda Village?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:44.26,00:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:51.86,00:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.28,00:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All... dead...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.53,00:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:05.66,00:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead?!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.58,00:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Plague... Plague did it...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:17.05,00:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My god !
Dialogue: 0,00:04:19.13,00:04:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This area's off limits! \NNo one goes through!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.14,00:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This road's closed until \Nthe epidemic is over.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.97,00:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Epidemic?! The hell with that!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.85,00:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:31.73,00:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, my scout saw a \Nstrange group of men
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.52,00:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ride toward Shimoda \NVillage late last night.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.86,00:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have something \Nto do with this
Dialogue: 0,00:04:43.16,00:04:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,epidemic so I came to \Ntell you, Chamberlain.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:45.70,00:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning what? That they spread a plague \Nas they passed through the village?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:51.42,00:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Why \Nwould they do that?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:54.71,00:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:56.88,00:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:02.43,00:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:04.26,00:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the order to \Nall of you Koga ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:06.76,00:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Shimoda Village and \Nfind what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:09.98,00:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:10.89,00:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing. If any of \Nyour people get infected...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:15.23,00:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:17.65,00:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The first group will follow the \NShirakawa River from the north.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:20.28,00:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The second will cross \NTaro Pass from the west.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:23.20,00:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll reach Shimoda Village \Nin about an hour. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.74,00:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikoza saw them. There were only eight. \NNo match for us.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:32.16,00:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our real enemy is this epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:35.17,00:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.43,00:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:56.52,00:05:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to leave \Nme behind, Hanza?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:59.82,00:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own \Nduties, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:02.86,00:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison tasting is very important. \NDon't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.78,00:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,While our lord is away from his \Ndomain, the work isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.08,00:06:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he returns...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.71,00:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of the Koga ninja!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:16.54,00:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot take you.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.54,00:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You could all be \Nkilled out there.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.09,00:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I just sit and \Nwait here alone?!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:41.73,00:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero's gotten even \Nmore beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:45.90,00:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason to pity her.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:48.24,00:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her destiny. \NShe must hate it.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.33,00:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Where are \NHikoza and the others?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:54.33,00:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They were right behind us. \NI'll have a look.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:12.64,00:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.52,00:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:47.22,00:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:10.28,00:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:21.46,00:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tessai!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:27.67,00:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are indeed a sorry sight.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:30.93,00:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.40,00:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that freak?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:48.82,00:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I don't want \Nto see him again, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:52.41,00:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you. I am \NKagero of the Koga ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:57.95,00:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei. Kibagami Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:02.50,00:09:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The town of Kakio is to the west. \NOur paths part here.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.18,00:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:59.56,00:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the way now, so...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:05.56,00:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:07.11,00:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it. Are we done now?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:11.61,00:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason we \Nshould kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:19.33,00:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to end this... \NI will!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:23.08,00:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:34.22,00:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange skill you have. But \Nit can't hurt my body.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:40.10,00:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.49,00:10:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Monster? Your \Nskin's starting to crumble!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:02.58,00:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:28.65,00:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid !
Dialogue: 0,00:11:30.77,00:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sword flew swift \Nas the wind itself and
Dialogue: 0,00:11:34.23,00:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,slashed your enemy like \Na cyclone's touch.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:38.86,00:11:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was no match for you. \NWhy don't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:42.62,00:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skills will be of great help \Nfor me to fight the likes of him.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:48.08,00:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking. Who'd want to \Nfight a monster like him again?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:53.67,00:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to. They \Nwon't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:56.63,00:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You just killed one of the \NEight Devils of Kimon.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.26,00:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't beat him \Nby yourself, though.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:07.68,00:12:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That Koga ninja woman... \NInteresting technique she uses.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.96,00:12:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Genma. All is \Nproceeding as planned.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:38.72,00:12:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It arrives from the Shogun of the \NDark by six tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.64,00:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Write \Nto him in return.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.60,00:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"We return in three days. There's \Nnothing to worry about."
Dialogue: 0,00:12:55.36,00:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At once.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:41.78,00:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.70,00:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No place in particular. You?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:49.99,00:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for somebody, and you \Nlook exactly like him, so...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.75,00:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Strangers can look alike. I'm \NKibagami Jubei, a wanderer...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.23,00:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was most certainly your face.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:15.40,00:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tessai was able to make \Nan impression of it.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:35.96,00:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me the hell alone!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:46.63,00:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A cast-off skin.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:48.76,00:14:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She shed it like a \Nsnake and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:54.31,00:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A gang of freaks, one and all.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:59.19,00:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no obligation. I just \Ndidn't want you to die yet.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:04.61,00:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these Eight \NDevils of Kimon?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:07.91,00:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of ninja who work \Nfor the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:10.07,00:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of the \NShogun of the Dark?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:11.70,00:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to rebuild the Toyotomi \Nclan, the former rulers of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:15.12,00:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He has 16 lords behind him and is \Ntrying to expand his influence.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:19.46,00:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The most dangerous enemy \Nof the Tokugawa Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:22.96,00:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is supported in the \Nshadows by the Eight Devils.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:27.09,00:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they up to \Nhere in Mochizuki?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:30.68,00:15:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I came here to find out. \NIt's a tough job.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:35.52,00:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you work for \Nme, for 100 ryo?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:39.73,00:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tokugawa spy wants \Nto hire a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:44.32,00:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I have no choice. \NIt's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:46.82,00:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I managed to make \Nit here to Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:50.53,00:15:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eight Devils killed everyone \Nelse in my party on our way here.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:53.12,00:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help by all means!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:56.75,00:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get away from them.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:59.75,00:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to fight \Nthem sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:02.09,00:16:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Join me. You can kill two \Nbirds with one stone, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.88,00:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. Now why don't \Nyou just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:12.39,00:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.52,00:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pity...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:20.06,00:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose your precious life.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:24.98,00:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:26.61,00:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what I speak of is literally of \Nlife or death importance to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:30.20,00:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that shuriken \Nwas poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.74,00:16:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't kill you instantly, \Nbut in a day and a
Dialogue: 0,00:16:37.29,00:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,night, when it starts to \Nwork, nothing can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.71,00:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you get the antidote. \NAnd only I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:46.17,00:16:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Work for me and I'll tell \Nyou the antidote along
Dialogue: 0,00:16:49.01,00:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with the hundred ryo \Nwhen the job is done.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.64,00:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:00.02,00:17:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.69,00:17:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me now. What's \Nthe antidote?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:05.61,00:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until you work for me. Kill \Nme and you've killed yourself!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:15.58,00:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll need the \Nantidote for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:17.99,00:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor boy... You've \Nso much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:20.96,00:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't the one that hit you.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:24.46,00:17:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw THAT one away.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:30.38,00:17:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:32.26,00:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibagami Jubei... You've lost... \Namateur!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:38.14,00:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dakuan. \NHow do you do?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:46.23,00:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Benisato...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:47.23,00:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This man, Kibagami Jubei, is a \Nremnant of the Shogunate's spies?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.36,00:17:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:53.70,00:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:55.91,00:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone interfered.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:57.49,00:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:01.95,00:18:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's a government spy, \Nhe'll show up here soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:06.38,00:18:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to kill him this time.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:08.59,00:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your \Nadvice to do that.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:15.59,00:18:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:17.55,00:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something \NI've been wondering.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:22.23,00:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you, by chance, the \Nninja who killed the chief
Dialogue: 0,00:18:25.35,00:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,retainers of the Yamashiro \Nclan five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:29.19,00:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He was supposedly a master \Nswordsman, like you.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:35.82,00:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The retainers had \Ngorged themselves with
Dialogue: 0,00:18:38.70,00:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,gold they secretly dug \Nout of a hidden mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:42.12,00:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The ninja must have killed \Nthem by order of the lord
Dialogue: 0,00:18:45.71,00:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,who wanted to report the \Nmine to the government.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:47.38,00:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if the government found \Nthe hidden gold mine first...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:51.30,00:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the lord would have \Nlost his fief.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:53.92,00:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But does that ninja know that after \Nthe retainers were killed...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:58.47,00:19:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the government received \Nno report about the mine?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:01.89,00:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:03.02,00:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If a government spy like you knows all \Nthat, then why don't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:09.40,00:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Even the government can't \Nmove without definite evidence.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:14.32,00:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spies tried many \Ntimes to infiltrate the
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.45,00:19:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,clan to find evidence, \Nbut none returned alive.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:20.99,00:19:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shogun of the Dark...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:22.37,00:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped them by \Nusing the Kimon ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:26.46,00:19:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the Shogun of the Dark \Nhelping the Yamashiro clan?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:30.33,00:19:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple. He wants the \Ngold mine for himself.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:35.59,00:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how he found the \Nmine before the government?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:41.22,00:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody gave him \Nthe information.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:43.76,00:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who was the leader of \Nthe ninja of the Yamashiro clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:48.60,00:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro... Genma?!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:51.81,00:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:54.53,00:19:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that. He isn't \Nin this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:58.57,00:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's still very much alive. \NAnd you'll see him soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:02.07,00:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro Genma is the boss \Nof the Kimon monsters.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:05.33,00:20:05.100,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.33,00:20:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud !
Dialogue: 0,00:20:08.41,00:20:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't trick me \Nthe same way again!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:10.46,00:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty. You'll \Nsoon know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:14.71,00:20:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must admit that you \Nand he share a strange fate.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:25.81,00:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You'd kill \Nyour own friend?!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:28.64,00:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The lord orders it! \NAs did our leader!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:33.61,00:20:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trick!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:35.15,00:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know the \Ntraitors' secret they want
Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.69,00:20:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to get rid of us by making \Nus kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:40.57,00:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a trap for all of us. \NShinkuro, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:45.49,00:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei... Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:47.54,00:20:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinkuro!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:49.71,00:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His word...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:51.46,00:20:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...is law!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:31.75,00:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I avenged Shinkuro and the others myself. \NGenma can't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:38.30,00:21:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting close. This place \Nis thick with ghosts and blood.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:42.51,00:21:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond lies Hell itself.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:49.22,00:21:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven must have sent \Nthis mist to help us.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.41,00:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:17.79,00:22:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Double damned mist!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:43.49,00:22:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he have \Ndodged Shijima's claw?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:15.35,00:23:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:16.48,00:23:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a voice \Nchanting the sutra.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:20.23,00:23:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was praying for \Nthe dead villagers.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:24.44,00:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know an epidemic \Nplagues this village?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:29.74,00:23:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor soul! You'll never \Nleave this village alive.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:34.83,00:23:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here now, let us go to the \Nland of Buddha together.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:44.46,00:23:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a \Ntraveling monk here?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:49.05,00:23:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll meet Buddha soon enough. \NI'll send him there.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:54.93,00:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a benevolent nun...
Dialogue: 0,00:24:05.07,00:24:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Another cast-off skin!
Dialogue: 0,00:24:17.50,00:24:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone... He uses a \Nstrange technique...
Dialogue: 0,00:24:32.14,00:24:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As do you. Very strange indeed !
Dialogue: 0,00:24:43.56,00:24:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me. Are there any others \Nwith you besides the monk?
Dialogue: 0,00:24:51.24,00:24:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. And not \Njust ten or twenty.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:54.74,00:24:57.100,Default,,0,0,0,,You can send a snake for \Neach and it won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,00:24:59.58,00:25:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,00:25:01.42,00:25:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll \Ntell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:05.29,00:25:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two. One's the traveling monk. \NThe other...
Dialogue: 0,00:25:09.13,00:25:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...is right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:12.93,00:25:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose the snakes. Down \Nto the last one!
Dialogue: 0,00:25:21.98,00:25:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be dead soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:27.78,00:25:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,00:25:47.25,00:25:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to answer.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:49.59,00:25:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in this village? \NTalk!
Dialogue: 0,00:26:10.99,00:26:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice failed. Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:13.99,00:26:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast another line onto your \Nneck, but you didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:17.99,00:26:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ln the end, just a \Nfoolish amateur.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:39.47,00:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! There's still time \Nto suck the poison out!
Dialogue: 0,00:26:42.98,00:26:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison doesn't work on me. \NMy body's immune to it.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:48.61,00:26:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've cleared \Nmy debt to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:51.11,00:26:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,00:26:54.07,00:26:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's Kagero, right? \NWhat are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:58.32,00:27:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:01.62,00:27:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't, then what the \Nhell am I doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,00:27:05.16,00:27:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to discover their plan.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:08.42,00:27:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,00:27:10.63,00:27:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too strong. \NThink this over.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:13.30,00:27:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:15.01,00:27:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no reason to \Ntake orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:21.85,00:27:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold a moment, Kunoichi of Koga.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:24.27,00:27:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dakuan. Why \Ndon't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,00:27:29.19,00:27:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is my \Ntrustworthy assistant.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:33.48,00:27:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on \Nhelping a government spy.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:35.99,00:27:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, quit complaining !
Dialogue: 0,00:27:38.28,00:27:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, woman?
Dialogue: 0,00:27:39.74,00:27:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our aims may differ, but we \Nthree share a common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:44.20,00:27:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And three is mightier than one.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:47.16,00:27:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I happen to have some \Ninformation you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:50.58,00:27:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such as who is giving \Nthem their orders.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:53.63,00:27:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you on the way.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:59.72,00:28:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I need no friends.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:01.47,00:28:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I may need your information.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:05.35,00:28:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:13.07,00:28:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My, she's a lovely, sexy \Nlittle thing, isn't she!
Dialogue: 0,00:28:18.20,00:28:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's running through that \Ntwisted skull of yours?
Dialogue: 0,00:28:21.49,00:28:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, that Kunoichi \Ncould prove very useful.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:25.24,00:28:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a technique to poison \Nthe man she sleeps with.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:29.58,00:28:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The big guy you killed had \Nbeen poisoned by her.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:20.22,00:29:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skill is as \Nmarvelous as ever.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:22.93,00:29:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No... He was able to kill a \Nmighty ninja like Tessai.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:26.35,00:29:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off guard. It's \Npossible he got away.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:30.98,00:29:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of you \Nwill check it out.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:33.23,00:29:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cautious one, Yurimaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:35.56,00:29:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an important mission. \NWe take every precaution.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:40.78,00:29:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:43.28,00:29:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:47.62,00:29:51.100,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurimaru, Benisato's death... \NHow fortunate for you!
Dialogue: 0,00:30:01.42,00:30:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only things he killed \Nwere the fish.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:03.63,00:30:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Otherwise we \Nwouldn't get our chance.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:06.18,00:30:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting quite \Ninteresting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:30:23.24,00:30:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Just as we thought?
Dialogue: 0,00:30:27.37,00:30:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They poisoned the wells \Nand killed the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:30.29,00:30:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then blamed it on plague.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:33.04,00:30:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A trick to keep the \Nvillagers away.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:37.17,00:30:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning something... \Nquite extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:52.81,00:30:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:55.85,00:30:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, just don't get \Nyourself involved too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:58.90,00:31:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It could prove fatal.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:22.25,00:31:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Guide the others.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:42.23,00:31:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:05.55,00:32:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't outrun them.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:09.38,00:32:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,00:32:28.95,00:32:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the pollen is mixed \Nwith a sleeping potion.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:31.57,00:32:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But how long will \Nit hold them back?
Dialogue: 0,00:32:34.58,00:32:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:36.75,00:32:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:37.96,00:32:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to hold them off \Ntill Jubei kills him!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:40.29,00:32:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:56.52,00:32:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Call off your bees!
Dialogue: 0,00:32:59.39,00:33:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you must \Nbeat me first.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:03.98,00:33:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,00:33:06.11,00:33:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I ran in \Nhere to escape you?
Dialogue: 0,00:33:09.61,00:33:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:10.61,00:33:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of questions for \Nyou, but no time to ask them.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:13.62,00:33:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just one thing. Tell \Nme, is Himuro Genma alive?
Dialogue: 0,00:33:17.54,00:33:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if he is?
Dialogue: 0,00:33:19.25,00:33:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask because I sent \Nhim to Hell before.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:22.04,00:33:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then I'll \Nhave to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:24.84,00:33:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Genma, I don't have the \Ntechnique to reincarnate myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:29.63,00:33:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation?
Dialogue: 0,00:33:39.68,00:33:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You've damaged the hive!
Dialogue: 0,00:33:58.87,00:34:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The second you come up for \Nair is the second you die!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:04.50,00:34:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mine! Keep \Nyour hands off him!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:08.04,00:34:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the \NKunoichi and the monk?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:09.80,00:34:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My bees should finish \Nthem off soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:23.10,00:34:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How far is he trying to run? \NWhat a poor loser!
Dialogue: 0,00:34:41.66,00:34:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he's fallen \Nvictim to the throat needle?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:55.13,00:34:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No... The bees in the hive are \Ntrying to escape the water.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:59.76,00:35:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Desperately stinging his body as \Nthey do so... Mushizo's lost.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:15.78,00:35:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Took his time about it, but \Nhe finally killed him.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:32.75,00:35:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation? Did he mean Himuro \NGenma's come back to life?
Dialogue: 0,00:35:39.39,00:35:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,00:35:54.07,00:35:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation? I've heard \Nabout the technique.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:59.11,00:36:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You must control your flesh and \Nblood down to the tiniest bones.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:04.49,00:36:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If your limbs or even your head were \Ncut off, you'd be able to rejoin them.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:10.79,00:36:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation... That's a \Ntechnique of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:14.00,00:36:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can never be achieved \Nby a human being.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:16.55,00:36:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well... That's \Na hell of a trick!
Dialogue: 0,00:36:19.26,00:36:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the Kimon monsters \Nare now all after you.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:23.72,00:36:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I can move easily.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:28.98,00:36:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky, \Nwe'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:34.27,00:36:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you join him?
Dialogue: 0,00:36:37.24,00:36:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He hired me... For 100 ryo.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:40.61,00:36:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mercenary ninja? One \Nwho'd do anything for money?
Dialogue: 0,00:36:44.37,00:36:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:46.24,00:36:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But he suckered me into it. \NTrapped me.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:50.92,00:36:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die of his \Npoison in half a day.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:55.05,00:36:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised me an antidote \Nalong with the gold.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:58.88,00:37:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I work for him. \NI can't back out now.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:03.35,00:37:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better run for it while \NI divert their attention.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:07.10,00:37:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that. I'd \Nowe you another debt.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:10.73,00:37:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about any debts.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:12.23,00:37:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told you I don't have \Nto take orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:15.61,00:37:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm ready \Nto die any moment.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:18.24,00:37:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. Stop pretending \Nyou're so tough.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:20.20,00:37:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:37:22.91,00:37:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this humid weather!
Dialogue: 0,00:37:25.24,00:37:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish a storm would come and \Ncool off that hot head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:33.88,00:37:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in no position \Nto worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:42.47,00:37:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm...
Dialogue: 0,00:37:45.76,00:37:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They came on the night \Nof that big storm...
Dialogue: 0,00:37:54.56,00:37:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where can I get a \Ngood look at this area?
Dialogue: 0,00:38:04.03,00:38:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How about there?
Dialogue: 0,00:38:05.41,00:38:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:06.66,00:38:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep looking !
Dialogue: 0,00:38:21.30,00:38:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanza...
Dialogue: 0,00:38:22.30,00:38:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:24.09,00:38:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanza!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:29.76,00:38:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a cliff in front of you! \NStop!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:33.39,00:38:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:48.49,00:38:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:49.62,00:38:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:38:58.54,00:39:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! They got you so soon? \NWe still had a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:08.14,00:39:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of blasted flesh, \Ngrilled to perfection...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:11.14,00:39:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a lovely smell.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:37.79,00:39:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... move...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:39.46,00:39:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:41.63,00:39:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault I fell \Nfor their trap.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:44.05,00:39:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,00:39:46.72,00:39:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! I don't \Nwant your help.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:49.34,00:39:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,00:39:59.10,00:40:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, grab it!
Dialogue: 0,00:40:14.29,00:40:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gonna hang onto me all day?
Dialogue: 0,00:40:34.14,00:40:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Utsutsu Mujuro. I've been \Nlonging to challenge you.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:45.53,00:40:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here for me. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:00.79,00:41:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You lured me here because I'm blind? \NIs that your plan?
Dialogue: 0,00:41:19.60,00:41:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me, \Nthen don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:23.35,00:41:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible. But maybe I can \Nturn your skill to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:02.48,00:42:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay back!
Dialogue: 0,00:42:10.90,00:42:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sight is your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:16.82,00:42:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,00:42:30.17,00:42:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,00:43:16.30,00:43:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The cargo from the ship that ran \Naground in the storm two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:19.60,00:43:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they're after.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:21.72,00:43:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They butchered the villagers \Nlike animals for it.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:38.74,00:43:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this road lead?
Dialogue: 0,00:43:46.100,00:43:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamberlain!
Dialogue: 0,00:43:48.92,00:43:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hyobu, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,00:43:50.34,00:43:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That the Koga ninja who went to investigate \NShimoda Village were wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,00:43:56.13,00:43:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:57.47,00:44:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?! This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:01.30,00:44:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my men to the \Nvillage immediately.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:03.77,00:44:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,00:44:04.93,00:44:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is serious \Nenough to jeopardize the
Dialogue: 0,00:44:08.14,00:44:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,safety of our clan, we \Nmust move very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:12.44,00:44:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how small clans \Nlike ours survive.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:14.86,00:44:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,00:44:16.24,00:44:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunoichi who survived is \Ncontinuing the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,00:44:19.82,00:44:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for her report.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:21.84,00:45:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those wheel tracks lead \Nto Kashima Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:25.64,00:45:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably going to \Ntransport the cargo out by boat.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:28.52,00:45:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop them...
Dialogue: 0,00:45:29.06,00:45:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,those dead villagers and the Koga \Nninja will never rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:39.53,00:45:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, you who labor \Nfor the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:43.57,00:45:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission could very \Nwell decide our fate!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:47.41,00:45:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship will reach \NMochizuki in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:50.50,00:45:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We must retrieve the \Ncargo at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:53.92,00:45:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood? At any cost!
Dialogue: 0,00:46:16.02,00:46:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The towns must have cleared out \Nout of fear of the epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:19.44,00:46:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One horse was enough to \Nscare them all away.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:27.07,00:46:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're still alive. \NI've been worried.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:31.08,00:46:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:33.54,00:46:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're waiting for a boat \Nto transport the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:37.38,00:46:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you check what the cargo is?
Dialogue: 0,00:46:39.46,00:46:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't reach it. But \NI can guess what it is.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:44.22,00:46:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I guessed before \NI came to Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:46.84,00:46:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:46:47.85,00:46:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,00:46:49.18,00:46:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that has \Nto do with your past.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:53.43,00:46:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gold, boy.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:55.44,00:46:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold produced from that \Nsecret Yamashiro mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:01.07,00:47:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship ran aground \Nduring the storm...
Dialogue: 0,00:47:03.24,00:47:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably on its way to the Shogun \Nof the Dark with caskets of gold.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:07.57,00:47:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold that's probably been \Nhidden for the last five years.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:12.16,00:47:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If it reaches his hands,
Dialogue: 0,00:47:14.37,00:47:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be powerful enough to \Ntopple the Tokugawa government...
Dialogue: 0,00:47:17.04,00:47:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...and plunge the country \Ninto another civil war.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:19.42,00:47:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,00:47:25.88,00:47:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakuan, you've got a tail.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:28.51,00:47:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:47:39.81,00:47:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,00:47:42.02,00:47:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling a Koga ninja \Nbird that's in this village.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:46.07,00:47:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling a bird? What for?
Dialogue: 0,00:47:48.03,00:47:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll carry my message to \Nthe castle chamberlain.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:50.87,00:47:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've discovered \Nwhat they're after.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:52.87,00:47:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ln two hours, his army \Nwill surround the town.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:57.08,00:47:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as easy as you think.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:59.00,00:48:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan will probably \Nignore this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:02.59,00:48:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,00:48:07.88,00:48:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The future of the \Nclan is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:09.72,00:48:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a power struggle between the \NTokugawa and the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:12.81,00:48:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If a small clan like the Mochizuki \Ngot involved, it'd be smashed !
Dialogue: 0,00:48:20.15,00:48:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See nothing, hear nothing. That's \Nthe best course for the clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:35.41,00:48:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out soon whether or \Nnot the Mochizuki will move.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:59.64,00:49:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:01.52,00:49:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:22.79,00:49:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi in Custody
Dialogue: 0,00:49:24.00,00:49:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi in Custody It must have \Nhappened when I went off for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:28.76,00:49:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunoichi in Custody
Dialogue: 0,00:49:30.09,00:49:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's most likely dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:33.93,00:49:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:36.97,00:49:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get no help from \Nthe Mochizuki clan.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:43.02,00:49:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for their trap.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:45.82,00:49:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:47.98,00:49:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What if their ship comes \Nwhile you're at it?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:50.57,00:49:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her alone! A dead Kunoichi \Nisn't that important!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:55.07,00:49:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not important compared \Nto the great mission?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:56.95,00:49:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as much of a \Nmonster as they are!
Dialogue: 0,00:49:58.95,00:50:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! When you fight monsters, you \Nbecome one yourself or you can't win!
Dialogue: 0,00:50:05.04,00:50:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn fool boy! Go ahead ! \NGO TO HELL!
Dialogue: 0,00:50:09.59,00:50:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... !
Dialogue: 0,00:50:56.34,00:50:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:59.72,00:51:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:19.58,00:51:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hard to kill, but... \NWoman, release his pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:46.48,00:51:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibagami Jubei?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:49.15,00:51:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But we've already \Nkilled them all.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:52.15,00:51:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! They still live.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:56.24,00:51:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:57.66,00:52:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are. Lure \Nthem there and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:02.41,00:52:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:03.66,00:52:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:10.33,00:52:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Never would I have \Nimagined to see him here.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:13.00,00:52:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing \Nyou again, Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:17.30,00:52:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma!
Dialogue: 0,00:52:23.85,00:52:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:26.10,00:52:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I take it the castle \Nretainers haven't taken any action?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:31.65,00:52:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two hours.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:34.61,00:52:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:39.95,00:52:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... You knew it was a trap, \Nbut you came to help me.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:43.66,00:52:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stupid. Why \Nrisk your life for me?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:47.08,00:52:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can't just \Ntoss aside my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:49.16,00:52:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrade?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:50.62,00:52:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We've saved each other \Nover and over since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:54.80,00:52:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a precious friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:05.43,00:53:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,00:53:06.72,00:53:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan is \Nstaying out of this one.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:09.35,00:53:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission is over.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:11.56,00:53:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't. I'm \Nstill in debt to you.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:16.69,00:53:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pay it back later.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:19.15,00:53:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you're dead !
Dialogue: 0,00:53:21.49,00:53:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll repay it here!
Dialogue: 0,00:53:33.33,00:53:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,00:53:41.22,00:53:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man told me how \Nto counteract the poison.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:45.97,00:53:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill poison with poison."
Dialogue: 0,00:53:48.14,00:53:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He said if you make love to a \Npoison-taster like me, you'll be cured.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:55.11,00:53:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me...
Dialogue: 0,00:54:52.91,00:54:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting ! Load \Nthe ship immediately!
Dialogue: 0,00:55:22.57,00:55:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Well, I warned \Nyou, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,00:55:25.86,00:55:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost. We'll never \Nbeat that many men.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:29.62,00:55:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to let them go. \NWe'll make our stand soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:34.58,00:55:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,00:55:35.100,00:55:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When they finish \Nloading the gold...
Dialogue: 0,00:55:38.83,00:55:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...go to the tower \Nand ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:41.05,00:55:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,While they're distracted, \NI'll sneak onboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:44.51,00:55:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're out at sea, \Nwe won't need any storm.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:47.38,00:55:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sink it myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:49.26,00:55:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,00:55:51.01,00:55:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you make \Nlove to that Kunoichi?
Dialogue: 0,00:55:56.27,00:56:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your damn business! \NNow get going !
Dialogue: 0,00:56:22.42,00:56:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma... Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:56:25.26,00:56:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When I die, I'll take \Nyou to hell with me!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:00.71,00:57:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan?! They're \Nmoving against them!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:08.59,00:57:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kunoichi! You've \Ndone a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:11.09,00:57:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, before they get away! \NWhere are the others?
Dialogue: 0,00:57:14.64,00:57:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. They've got \Nthis place surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:18.02,00:57:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hurry!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:38.29,00:57:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,00:57:48.13,00:57:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:51.26,00:57:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:53.39,00:57:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Sakaki Hyobu \Ndied two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:11.78,00:58:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him personally.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:14.11,00:58:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma!
Dialogue: 0,00:58:40.35,00:58:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please get aboard \Nthe ship quickly.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:43.77,00:58:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The retainers of the Shogun \Nof the Dark are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:48.19,00:58:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Jubei to me. Upon my \Nhonor, I will not fail.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:53.36,00:58:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please grant me this one wish.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:00.99,00:59:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then. Go.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:30.77,00:59:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this. Don't shame me \Nany more than you already have.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:37.24,00:59:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you are Genma?
Dialogue: 0,00:59:39.41,00:59:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mochizuki clan \Nsuspects nothing, correct?
Dialogue: 0,00:59:42.91,00:59:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. All is well.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:44.91,00:59:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done a splendid job. I \Nadmire you Devils of Kimon.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:49.42,00:59:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shogun of the \NDark will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,01:00:25.62,01:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Writhe in pain before you die.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:03.62,01:01:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurimaru seems to have \Nsuffered some ill fortune!
Dialogue: 0,01:01:06.62,01:01:09.100,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless of him to \Nhave fallen into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:11.46,01:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your own fault, Yurimaru.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:17.67,01:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:21.80,01:01:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,01:01:32.65,01:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,01:01:38.69,01:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,01:01:40.49,01:01:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to come.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:43.28,01:01:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted... to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,01:01:50.50,01:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,01:01:52.92,01:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't treat me like \Nsome poison-taster...
Dialogue: 0,01:01:56.67,01:01:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...but like a normal woman.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:52.06,01:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei... I'm glad... \NI met you...
Dialogue: 0,01:04:32.12,01:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma, with the gold's help our \Ndream will soon be reality.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:37.75,01:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our" dream?
Dialogue: 0,01:04:38.79,01:04:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our great dream to topple the Shogunate \Nand restore the reign of the Toyotomi.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:44.92,01:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,01:04:46.84,01:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How we, the former retainers \Nof Toyotomi, have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:50.76,01:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it'll be the Tokugawa who \Nsuffer the agony and torment.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:54.35,01:05:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use the gold to buy advanced weapons \Nfrom Spain and defeat the Tokugawa.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:00.15,01:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the dream of all of us who \Nwork for the Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:05.48,01:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:08.36,01:05:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,01:05:09.82,01:05:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:11.57,01:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your tongue! \NYou're a mere ninja!
Dialogue: 0,01:05:14.66,01:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is different.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:16.62,01:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The gold isn't going to \Nthe Shogun of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:19.58,01:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,01:05:20.33,01:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Devils of Kimon, \Nwill take the gold.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:22.67,01:05:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You impudent... !
Dialogue: 0,01:05:26.21,01:05:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use it to organize the most \Npowerful army of ninja ever.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:30.55,01:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll rule the country with \Nterror and power from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:35.47,01:05:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who opposes me, \NTokugawa or Toyotomi...
Dialogue: 0,01:05:38.43,01:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...even the Shogun of the \NDark himself, shall die.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:42.90,01:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning the true Shogun of the Dark... \Nwill be me.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:04.54,01:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, you're here! I was \Njust wishing you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:10.38,01:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:11.97,01:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:13.64,01:06:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your help, sinking a big \Nship like this would be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:25.52,01:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic old fool!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:28.23,01:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:39.79,01:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,01:06:41.58,01:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire in the hold ! \NWe're gonna sink!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:44.75,01:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:46.58,01:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! It's a sea of flame!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:48.80,01:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it out! Fight it!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:51.55,01:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:53.93,01:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Run!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:04.31,01:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Genma!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:06.23,01:07:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass this message to everyone:
Dialogue: 0,01:07:07.81,01:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Abandon ship and hide yourselves. \NI'll call for you someday."
Dialogue: 0,01:07:12.99,01:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:53.61,01:07:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:56.86,01:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you brought back some \Ndevils from your trip to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:08.96,01:08:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibagami Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,01:08:10.92,01:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've finished \Nyou with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:14.55,01:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your whining. \NIt's too late.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:19.09,01:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to avenge \Nthe Kunoichi Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,01:08:22.81,01:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She was trash in comparison \Nto what I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,01:08:30.06,01:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You alone I can't forgive!
Dialogue: 0,01:09:22.49,01:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't kill you yet. Not \Nbefore I make you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:26.16,01:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you pay for \Nsmashing my dream.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:28.62,01:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream? That you were going to \Nbe the true Shogun of the Dark?
Dialogue: 0,01:09:34.38,01:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:36.34,01:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you became shogun, you'd \Nmake this a world of devils.
Dialogue: 0,01:09:42.05,01:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you enjoy their company so much... \Nthen go back to hell!
Dialogue: 0,01:10:04.03,01:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,01:10:08.95,01:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:15.46,01:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all people \Nshould know by now...
Dialogue: 0,01:10:21.26,01:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am immortal.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:27.26,01:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,01:10:40.90,01:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep coming \Nback to life...
Dialogue: 0,01:10:44.95,01:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I'll kill you as \Nmany times as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:00.57,01:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:47.49,01:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Genma! HERE YOU DIE!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:49.01,01:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:50.38,01:13:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be rid of the \Npoison, thanks to Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,01:13:54.93,01:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The combination of a poison-tasting \NKunoichi and a talented lone wolf
Dialogue: 0,01:13:59.35,01:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,worked out even better \Nthan I had planned.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:01.89,01:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:07.86,01:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm sorry about losing Kagero. \NA real pity, that!
Dialogue: 0,01:14:12.66,01:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a scant few \Nmoments, she was able to
Dialogue: 0,01:14:15.91,01:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,be an ordinary girl and \Nmake love with you.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:19.91,01:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that part of your plan, too?
Dialogue: 0,01:14:21.91,01:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. To read and control peoples' \Nhearts is the true secret of the ninja.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:28.75,01:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, only true sincerity \Ncan move the human heart.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:33.38,01:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A twisted old bastard \Nlike me couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:36.39,01:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hell of a guy. \NI really admire you.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:40.14,01:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I'll be waiting \Nin Edo with your 100 ryo.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:43.14,01:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get it, if \Nyou're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:51.90,01:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes us even. Now \Nnever cross my path again.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:56.41,01:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've beaten me. I thought I'd \Nshut your mouth in Edo, but...
Dialogue: 0,01:15:00.12,01:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, in your condition you likely \Nwon't even make it to the shore.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:04.17,01:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will end \Njust as I planned.
